---
title: Fillet Steak, Creamy Bacon-Mushroom Sauce & Golden Fries with Spiced Apple & Pear Crumble for Dessert
description: Show Dad the love this Father’s Day by surprising him with a sublime two-course meal. Dish up tender beef fillet with a delicious mushroom-bacon sauce, plus golden fries and veggies. Then, for dessert, whip up our heavenly apple and pear crumble.
